        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Slow Cooker Beef Stroganoff. A British home-cook's dish — the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "It runs in the slow cooker so the work is at the start of the day and the dinner cooks itself."
